  "content": "\n                <p>Stiff person syndrome (SPS) is a rare disorder that manifests with progressive muscle stiffness and rigidity. It is caused by an autoimmune process in which <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1fY2Oo\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-lxid=\"x50Emg\" data-section-id=\"R_XlL00\" data-sxid=\"R_XlL00\" data-title=\"QWRhcHRpdmUgaW1tdW5lIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgSW1tdW5vZ2xvYnVsaW5z\" id=\"L3216f516bf3a823b7250395df79b1fa5\" data-source=\"L3216f516bf3a823b7250395df79b1fa5\">antibodies</span> are formed against <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"u5bpN8\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z45efac2748714624ec10ed2805c93df1\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"VCcGIe0\" data-sxid=\"VCcGIe0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXVyb3RyYW5zbWl0dGVycw==\" id=\"L4180aabf00fedd7da770c17abbf729aa\" data-source=\"L4180aabf00fedd7da770c17abbf729aa\">glutamic acid decarboxylase</span> (<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"G9cBKe0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QW4gYWJicmV2aWF0aW9uIHRoYXQgY2FuIHJlZmVyIHRvOjxicj4NCjEuIEdlbmVyYWxpemVkIGFueGlldHkgZGlzb3JkZXI8YnI+DQoyLiBHbHV0YW1pYyBhY2lkIGRlY2FyYm94eWxhc2U8L3A+\" id=\"L0dfe9720225dfc2bab9f1bf30b80ada2\" data-source=\"L0dfe9720225dfc2bab9f1bf30b80ada2\">GAD</span>) or another protein in the <span class=\"nowrap\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6fbjMG\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6625804b83e4ca0c92651a2763692086\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"VCcGIe0\" data-sxid=\"VCcGIe0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXVyb3RyYW5zbWl0dGVycw==\" id=\"L83de778d38d5b470e843c60a26372012\" data-source=\"L83de778d38d5b470e843c60a26372012\">gamma-aminobutyric</span></span> acid (<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6fbjMG\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6625804b83e4ca0c92651a2763692086\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"VCcGIe0\" data-sxid=\"VCcGIe0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXVyb3RyYW5zbWl0dGVycw==\" id=\"Ldf8e298730883eeedfc6346445ad6951\" data-source=\"Ldf8e298730883eeedfc6346445ad6951\">GABA</span>) synthesis pathway. This leads to reduced levels of <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6fbjMG\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6625804b83e4ca0c92651a2763692086\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"VCcGIe0\" data-sxid=\"VCcGIe0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXVyb3RyYW5zbWl0dGVycw==\" id=\"L5c44ae1964e15623390ea7d5494c19a1\" data-source=\"L5c44ae1964e15623390ea7d5494c19a1\">GABA</span>, which then causes loss of <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6SXj0B\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z0111aade770ed6f7d136b455de1d6c1f\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"1Cc2Ie0\" data-sxid=\"1Cc2Ie0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXJ2ZSB0aXNzdWU=\" id=\"L7a8db08ac1996ae4e2ef3c7b64b56642\" data-source=\"L7a8db08ac1996ae4e2ef3c7b64b56642\">CNS</span> inhibition and increasing muscle stiffness. SPS is associated with autoimmune disorders (particularly <span class=\"nowrap\">type 1</span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"a40Q3T\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-lxid=\"3g0SE2\" data-title=\"RGlhYmV0ZXMgbWVsbGl0dXM=\" id=\"L85c70d8347322a28839628c4cc9885da\" data-source=\"L85c70d8347322a28839628c4cc9885da\">diabetes mellitus</span>). Less commonly, it occurs as a paraneoplastic process. Treatment of SPS consists of symptomatic treatment with <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"zn0rDg\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zf884f2b003a5889d564461961fb1abc3\" data-learningcard-id=\"CN0qWg\" data-lxid=\"CN0qWg\" data-section-id=\"L11whf0\" data-sxid=\"L11whf0\" data-title=\"U2VkYXRpdmUtaHlwbm90aWMgZHJ1Z3Mg4oaSIEJlbnpvZGlhemVwaW5lcw==\" id=\"L28a49c9d1a3d7ad09d72370cb4b52c6c\" data-source=\"L28a49c9d1a3d7ad09d72370cb4b52c6c\">benzodiazepines</span> and <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"An0RDg\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zbb4c182861fab40f80aafafb0200fbc5\" data-learningcard-id=\"DN01Wg\" data-lxid=\"DN01Wg\" data-title=\"U2tlbGV0YWwgbXVzY2xlIHJlbGF4YW50cw==\" id=\"L1f76ef4d5231027cda1fd2398bb3c822\" data-source=\"L1f76ef4d5231027cda1fd2398bb3c822\">muscle relaxants</span> as well as immune modulation therapy with IVIG and <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"so0tWS\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zbe2f99ecf3c73cc831a5c78ef2226ffd\" data-learningcard-id=\"qM0Cpg\" data-lxid=\"qM0Cpg\" data-title=\"SW1tdW5vc3VwcHJlc3NhbnRz\" id=\"L031b2f2358c9576dd83f08068dcc4b59\" data-source=\"L031b2f2358c9576dd83f08068dcc4b59\">immunosuppressants</span>. Prognosis is poor, with most patients experiencing progressive gait disorders and disability.</p>\n<!--no-condensed--><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Autoimmune disease: <span class=\"wichtig\"><span class=\"nowrap\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"q5XCOA\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z41e465c56de7c45d6232254e837b762a\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-lxid=\"3g0SE2\" data-section-id=\"vI0Aeh\" data-sxid=\"vI0Aeh\" data-title=\"RGlhYmV0ZXMgbWVsbGl0dXMg4oaSIERpYWdub3Npcw==\" id=\"Ldb42067ec7e792dd6a031c35f876d936\" data-source=\"Ldb42067ec7e792dd6a031c35f876d936\">Anti-GAD</span></span></span> or <span class=\"wichtig\"><span class=\"nowrap\">anti-amphiphysin</span></span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1fY2Oo\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-lxid=\"x50Emg\" data-section-id=\"R_XlL00\" data-sxid=\"R_XlL00\" data-title=\"QWRhcHRpdmUgaW1tdW5lIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgSW1tdW5vZ2xvYnVsaW5z\" id=\"L7a9424686cf8e07b19f2d4f9a9f247e0\" data-source=\"L7a9424686cf8e07b19f2d4f9a9f247e0\">antibodies</span> (<span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6dee07cab92e13d1f6baa3a3ce402f23\" data-learningcard-id=\"8K0ORS\" data-lxid=\"8K0ORS\" data-title=\"UHJvdGVpbnMgYW5kIHBlcHRpZGVz\" id=\"L6d568748ab7fc8140d932b5ea9707757\" data-source=\"L6d568748ab7fc8140d932b5ea9707757\">proteins</span> involved in the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6fbjMG\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6625804b83e4ca0c92651a2763692086\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"VCcGIe0\" data-sxid=\"VCcGIe0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXVyb3RyYW5zbWl0dGVycw==\" id=\"L875a04321d84e022a3371be1681a3325\" data-source=\"L875a04321d84e022a3371be1681a3325\">GABA</span> synthesis pathway) are present in <span class=\"nowrap\">approx. 70%</span> of cases.</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z61f39ffb332429aee46c317f01ac1dc1\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-lxid=\"x50Emg\" data-section-id=\"Q_XuL00\" data-sxid=\"Q_XuL00\" data-title=\"QWRhcHRpdmUgaW1tdW5lIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgQiBjZWxscyAoQiBseW1waG9jeXRlcyk=\" id=\"Lcd2ea5b64ceb424a1bd12c64bd401f20\" data-source=\"Lcd2ea5b64ceb424a1bd12c64bd401f20\">Antibody production</span> may be:<ul>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"lj0v0T\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBkZXNjcmlwdG9yIGZvciBhIGNvbmRpdGlvbiB3aXRoIGFuIHVua25vd24gY2F1c2Ugb3IgcGF0aG9waHlzaW9sb2d5LjwvcD4=\" id=\"L9e1ad14e96f67083bf86b051534a6372\" data-source=\"L9e1ad14e96f67083bf86b051534a6372\">Idiopathic</span></li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"wichtig\">Paraneoplastic</span> (rare; secondary to <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"4M03Kg\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z3186a2e5e91124c9021effe4344433c7\" data-learningcard-id=\"_k05qT\" data-lxid=\"_k05qT\" data-title=\"QnJlYXN0IGNhbmNlcg==\" id=\"L6078118eeb524b3119458222a66c3035\" data-source=\"L6078118eeb524b3119458222a66c3035\">breast cancer</span>, <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"sk0t6T\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z3ff7ac92fae21c5ca2363549c47bb7e7\" data-learningcard-id=\"nh07ef\" data-lxid=\"nh07ef\" data-title=\"THVuZyBjYW5jZXI=\" id=\"L6ab8da72207a197e20510280425567a7\" data-source=\"L6ab8da72207a197e20510280425567a7\">lung cancer</span>, and <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"7RX4oB\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2586a20a2f640af294a4d86b9f8439d0\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-lxid=\"WM0Png\" data-section-id=\"azXQr00\" data-sxid=\"azXQr00\" data-title=\"R2VuZXJhbCBvbmNvbG9neSDihpIgTm9tZW5jbGF0dXJl\" id=\"Lac94c800e34b44574e3e852736e1b444\" data-source=\"Lac94c800e34b44574e3e852736e1b444\">lymphoma</span>)</li>\n<li>Associated with autoimmune diseases (<span class=\"nowrap\">type 1</span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"a40Q3T\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-lxid=\"3g0SE2\" data-title=\"RGlhYmV0ZXMgbWVsbGl0dXM=\" id=\"L77def8e3ea086ce9a35412f992c74679\" data-source=\"L77def8e3ea086ce9a35412f992c74679\">diabetes mellitus</span>, thyroiditis, <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"eM0xng\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z615a01f03501bbd7b3655e4bac005374\" data-learningcard-id=\"7k046T\" data-lxid=\"7k046T\" data-title=\"Vml0aWxpZ28=\" id=\"Lff778cc986447e603e347f4fd4be0fed\" data-source=\"Lff778cc986447e603e347f4fd4be0fed\">vitiligo</span>, <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6ZajcQ\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z23d6b596faa18f57dcb166c93439d25e\" data-learningcard-id=\"6R0jLf\" data-lxid=\"6R0jLf\" data-section-id=\"wHahsN\" data-sxid=\"wHahsN\" data-title=\"Vml0YW1pbiBCMTIgZGVmaWNpZW5jeSDihpIgUGF0aG9waHlzaW9sb2d5\" id=\"Lacdc1f49095348c87ddcfc759308f35a\" data-source=\"Lacdc1f49095348c87ddcfc759308f35a\">pernicious anemia</span>)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"unwichtig\">References:<span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"gHaFpN\" data-page=\"\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span> </span></p>\n\n<!--no-condensed--><p class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"wichtig\"><span class=\"nowrap\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"q5XCOA\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z41e465c56de7c45d6232254e837b762a\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-lxid=\"3g0SE2\" data-section-id=\"vI0Aeh\" data-sxid=\"vI0Aeh\" data-title=\"RGlhYmV0ZXMgbWVsbGl0dXMg4oaSIERpYWdub3Npcw==\" id=\"L9a10689dc3eaa3f6617ef0ac5fee62c4\" data-source=\"L9a10689dc3eaa3f6617ef0ac5fee62c4\">Anti-GAD</span></span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1fY2Oo\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-lxid=\"x50Emg\" data-section-id=\"R_XlL00\" data-sxid=\"R_XlL00\" data-title=\"QWRhcHRpdmUgaW1tdW5lIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgSW1tdW5vZ2xvYnVsaW5z\" id=\"L51183838911592ff90af63a49be989fd\" data-source=\"L51183838911592ff90af63a49be989fd\">antibodies</span></span> <span class=\"nowrap\">→ decreased</span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"G9cBKe0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QW4gYWJicmV2aWF0aW9uIHRoYXQgY2FuIHJlZmVyIHRvOjxicj4NCjEuIEdlbmVyYWxpemVkIGFueGlldHkgZGlzb3JkZXI8YnI+DQoyLiBHbHV0YW1pYyBhY2lkIGRlY2FyYm94eWxhc2U8L3A+\" id=\"Le747ac08192e17307089935312e1d0a1\" data-source=\"Le747ac08192e17307089935312e1d0a1\">GAD</span> <span class=\"nowrap\">→ decreased</span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6fbjMG\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6625804b83e4ca0c92651a2763692086\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"VCcGIe0\" data-sxid=\"VCcGIe0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXVyb3RyYW5zbWl0dGVycw==\" id=\"Lcd86024a57af7ce0c256c163234645ee\" data-source=\"Lcd86024a57af7ce0c256c163234645ee\">GABA</span> <span class=\"nowrap\">→ loss</span> of <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6SXj0B\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z0111aade770ed6f7d136b455de1d6c1f\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"1Cc2Ie0\" data-sxid=\"1Cc2Ie0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXJ2ZSB0aXNzdWU=\" id=\"Ld6f66330fba6e5e5d461451b55e94035\" data-source=\"Ld6f66330fba6e5e5d461451b55e94035\">CNS</span> inhibition <span class=\"nowrap\">→ increased</span> muscle tone and <span class=\"wichtig\">rigidity</span></p>\n<p class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"unwichtig\">References:<span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"gHaFpN\" data-page=\"\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></span></p>\n\n<!--no-condensed--><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Generalized increase in <span class=\"wichtig\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"FRXgKB\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6f7ea6c70fce86b21d8ffeb1772bdfe0\" data-learningcard-id=\"so0tWS\" data-lxid=\"so0tWS\" data-section-id=\"HzcK8U0\" data-sxid=\"HzcK8U0\" data-title=\"TXVzY2xlIHRpc3N1ZSDihpIgU2tlbGV0YWwgbXVzY2xl\" id=\"L9378f408507be045ee6c3f5ee7efa56e\" data-source=\"L9378f408507be045ee6c3f5ee7efa56e\">skeletal muscle</span> rigidity</span> (hands, feet, and face remain unaffected); particularly in the muscles of the <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z3538c7d0d3c09a64652ecccc7971d5ae\" data-learningcard-id=\"xo0EVS\" data-lxid=\"xo0EVS\" data-section-id=\"h_ccLU0\" data-sxid=\"h_ccLU0\" data-title=\"QW5hdG9taWNhbCB0ZXJtcyDihpIgU3RhbmRhcmQgYW5hdG9taWNhbCBwb3NpdGlvbg==\" id=\"L6994daa72d10c590a51a78b5d90fd676\" data-source=\"L6994daa72d10c590a51a78b5d90fd676\">proximal</span> extremities, neck and back.</li>\n<li>Progressive rigidity may lead to lumbar or cervical <span class=\"wichtig\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"94cNlc0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zc2a4f00c98526015f114c603b39fa043\" data-learningcard-id=\"E6085S\" data-lxid=\"E6085S\" data-section-id=\"rucfsV0\" data-sxid=\"rucfsV0\" data-title=\"VmVydGVicmFsIGNvbHVtbiDihpIgR3Jvc3MgYW5hdG9teQ==\" id=\"L6835aa4d570851c657228e9eae6a8efe\" data-source=\"L6835aa4d570851c657228e9eae6a8efe\">hyperlordosis</span></span> as well as gait abnormalities that may, in turn, cause falls and <span class=\"wichtig\"><span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"T3063f\" data-lxid=\"T3063f\" data-title=\"R2VuZXJhbCBwcmluY2lwbGVzIG9mIGZyYWN0dXJlcw==\" id=\"L4c3fdd6b8a5e97f72fc13c8263a426cb\" data-source=\"L4c3fdd6b8a5e97f72fc13c8263a426cb\">fractures</span></span>.</li>\n<li>Episodic <span class=\"wichtig\">painful muscle spasms</span> triggered by external (e.g., noise) and internal (e.g., emotional upset) stimuli <span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Ecdd50f761440be4bf1aea2c170d8b304\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li>Partial SPS: disease variant in which symptoms are limited to one extremity</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"unwichtig\">References:<span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"gHaFpN\" data-page=\"\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span> </span></p>\n\n<!--no-condensed--><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>\n<span class=\"leitwort\">Laboratory findings</span><ul>\n<li>Detection of <span class=\"nowrap\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"q5XCOA\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z41e465c56de7c45d6232254e837b762a\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-lxid=\"3g0SE2\" data-section-id=\"vI0Aeh\" data-sxid=\"vI0Aeh\" data-title=\"RGlhYmV0ZXMgbWVsbGl0dXMg4oaSIERpYWdub3Npcw==\" id=\"L353ec7ec611beb223a7b7f1de0534382\" data-source=\"L353ec7ec611beb223a7b7f1de0534382\">anti-GAD</span></span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1fY2Oo\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-lxid=\"x50Emg\" data-section-id=\"R_XlL00\" data-sxid=\"R_XlL00\" data-title=\"QWRhcHRpdmUgaW1tdW5lIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgSW1tdW5vZ2xvYnVsaW5z\" id=\"Laae3b806708f4db8b5434e3e84d405e2\" data-source=\"Laae3b806708f4db8b5434e3e84d405e2\">antibodies</span> (in <span class=\"wichtig\"><span class=\"nowrap\">60–90%</span></span> of cases)</li>\n<li>Paraneoplastic SPS is usually <span class=\"nowrap\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"q5XCOA\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z41e465c56de7c45d6232254e837b762a\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-lxid=\"3g0SE2\" data-section-id=\"vI0Aeh\" data-sxid=\"vI0Aeh\" data-title=\"RGlhYmV0ZXMgbWVsbGl0dXMg4oaSIERpYWdub3Npcw==\" id=\"L57ec4a5fd1d6931ec83799a363deddb2\" data-source=\"L57ec4a5fd1d6931ec83799a363deddb2\">anti-GAD</span></span> <span class=\"nowrap\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1fY2Oo\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-lxid=\"x50Emg\" data-section-id=\"R_XlL00\" data-sxid=\"R_XlL00\" data-title=\"QWRhcHRpdmUgaW1tdW5lIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgSW1tdW5vZ2xvYnVsaW5z\" id=\"L2797ab8ed2c0a1b55935ae9bbb69322f\" data-source=\"L2797ab8ed2c0a1b55935ae9bbb69322f\">antibody</span>-negative</span>; <span class=\"nowrap\">anti-amphiphysin</span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"1fY2Oo\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-lxid=\"x50Emg\" data-section-id=\"R_XlL00\" data-sxid=\"R_XlL00\" data-title=\"QWRhcHRpdmUgaW1tdW5lIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgSW1tdW5vZ2xvYnVsaW5z\" id=\"La43eb43e4b19fad3a07a072cf0d81d60\" data-source=\"La43eb43e4b19fad3a07a072cf0d81d60\">antibodies</span> may be detected in some cases</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"leitwort\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"rMYfJp\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z820063be8718807899bf632781a10495\" data-learningcard-id=\"Cn0qvg\" data-lxid=\"Cn0qvg\" data-section-id=\"9bcNDa0\" data-sxid=\"9bcNDa0\" data-title=\"TmV1cm9waHlzaW9sb2dpY2FsIGRpYWdub3N0aWNzIOKGkiBFbGVjdHJvbXlvZ3JhcGh5IChFTUcp\" id=\"La0d167